{"id": "art-939", "label": "Art. 939", "title": "Art. 939: Internarea provizorie nevoluntară", "slug": "art-939", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1861692161\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1090\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1861692161\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 939:\nInternarea provizorie nevoluntar&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_762794952\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1089\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_762794952\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul în care este necesar&#259; observarea mai îndelungat&#259;\na st&#259;rii de s&#259;n&#259;tate a celui a c&#259;rui ocrotire se cere, ce\nnu poate fi realizat&#259; decât prin internarea sa provizorie într-o\ninstitu&#355;ie sanitar&#259; de specialitate, iar acesta refuz&#259;\ninternarea, procurorul, la sesizarea medicului care efectueaz&#259; evaluarea\nmedical&#259;, va solicita motivat instan&#355;ei de tutel&#259; luarea acestei\nm&#259;suri.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1785142392\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1088\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1785142392\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)M&#259;sura se dispune numai dup&#259; ascultarea\npersoanei a c&#259;rei ocrotire se cere. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 940 alin. (3)\nteza final&#259; &#351;i ale art. 940 alin. (4) r&#259;mân aplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1673464272\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1087\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1673464272\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Instan&#355;a, solicitând &#351;i concluziile\nprocurorului, va putea dispune, motivat &#351;i propor&#355;ional cu scopul\nurm&#259;rit, internarea provizorie nevoluntar&#259; a celui a c&#259;rui\nocrotire se cere, pentru cel mult 20 de zile, într-o institu&#355;ie\nsanitar&#259; de specialitate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_916231709\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1086\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_916231709\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Instan&#355;a se pronun&#355;&#259; prin încheiere\nexecutorie, care este supus&#259; numai apelului, în termen de 3 zile, care\ncurge de la pronun&#355;are pentru cei prezen&#355;i &#351;i de la comunicare\npentru cei lips&#259;. Apelul se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; în termen de 5 zile de\nla formularea acestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_45435135\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1085\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_45435135\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 940 alin. (2) &#351;i (7)\nr&#259;mân aplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_602279208\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1084\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_602279208\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În cazul în care înainte de expirarea duratei\nintern&#259;rii provizorii nevoluntare se constat&#259; c&#259; aceasta nu mai\neste necesar&#259;, institu&#355;ia sanitar&#259; de specialitate\nprocedeaz&#259; de îndat&#259; la externarea persoanei a c&#259;rei ocrotire se\ncere.</span></p>"}